== 建造 ==
在建造初期，[[科欽造船廠|科欽造船廠]]便遇上第一個問題—缺乏[[钢|鋼材]]。由於俄羅斯無力供應印度所需要的{{link-en|ABA鋼材|ABS Steels}}，{{link-en|印度國防冶金研究實驗室|Defence Metallurgical Research Laboratory}}（DMRL）便與[[印度鋼鐵管理局|印度鋼鐵管理局]]（SAIL）合作，創建位於印度的鋼鐵生產設施，<ref name=hindu-float/><ref name=hindu-keel>{{cite web |url=http://www.hindu.com/2008/09/29/stories/2008092955681400.htm |title=Keel-laying of indigenous aircraft carrier in December |publisher=Hindu.com |date=29 September 2008 |accessdate=1 February 2011 |archive-date=2010-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100725081847/http://www.hindu.com/2008/09/29/stories/2008092955681400.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 負責生產航空母艦所需要的ABA特種鋼材，維克蘭特的建造工作才得以進行。

2009年2月28日，工作人員在維克蘭特號上開始安放龍骨，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ndtv.com/convergence/ndtv/story.aspx?id=NEWEN20090085124 |title=India overhauls coastal security, Navy gets charge |publisher=NDTV.com |date=28 February 2009 |accessdate=1 February 2011 |archive-date=2012-09-08 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120908225312/http://www.ndtv.com/convergence/ndtv/story.aspx?id=NEWEN20090085124 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://en.rian.ru/world/20090226/120325539.html |title=India to lay keel of new aircraft carrier on Saturday | World | RIA Novosti |publisher=En.rian.ru |date=26 February 2009 |accessdate=1 February 2011 |archive-date=2011-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605175227/http://en.rian.ru/world/20090226/120325539.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>由於建造工作是採用模組化結構，所以維克蘭特號上也將有874塊模組連接在一起。在鋪設龍骨的時候，維克蘭特已經有423塊超過8,000噸的模組完成連接。<ref name=Herald_Elite_club>{{cite news|title=India joins elite warships club|url=http://archive.deccanherald.com/Content/Mar12009/scroll20090301121399.asp|accessdate=15 July 2012|newspaper=[[Deccan_Herald|Deccan Herald]]|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.deccanherald.com%2FContent%2FMar12009%2Fscroll20090301121399.asp&date=2012-07-15|archivedate=2012-07-15|date=1 March 2009|deadurl=yes}}</ref>雖然印度海軍曾希望維克蘭特號在2010年便能下水，但實際上在建造過程中[[科欽造船廠|科欽造船廠]]便因為多次個別原因將維克蘭特從[[旱塢|旱塢]]拖出，以騰出空間予其他建造工作進行，再加上缺乏建造經驗的緣故，導致完工時間不斷拖延。最終{{link-en|印度內閣安全委員會|Cabinet Committee on Security}}（CCS）將試航時間定在2013年，並在2014年內完成。<ref>{{cite web |author=Sandeep Unnithan |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=29613&sectionid=4&issueid=93&Itemid=1 |title=Keel laying of indigenous aircraft carrier next week |publisher=Indiatoday.intoday.in |date=18 February 2009 |accessdate=1 February 2011 |archive-date=2009-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727031555/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=29613&sectionid=4&issueid=93&Itemid=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report_indigenous-aircraft-carrier-s-nucleus-ready_1448720 |title=Indigenous Aircraft Carrier’s nucleus ready - India - DNA |publisher=Dnaindia.com |date=7 October 2010 |accessdate=1 February 2011 |archive-date=2011-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110210144906/http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report_indigenous-aircraft-carrier-s-nucleus-ready_1448720 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年3月，根據媒體報導，建造項目由於廠商艾列孔工程（Elecon Engineering）在齒輪箱的推進軸上的設計出現問題<ref name=hindu-schedule>{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-kerala/article1530996.ece|title=Indigenous aircraft carrier a year behind schedule|publisher=The Hindu|date=12 March 2011|accessdate=31 December 2011|archive-date=2013-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214055340/http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-kerala/article1530996.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>，再加上諸如柴油發電機等方面的零件也在安裝上出現事故<ref name=hindu-arihant>{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/article2681534.ece|title=INS Arihant on track|publisher=The Hindu|date=3 December 2011|accessdate=31 December 2011|archive-date=2013-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214055336/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/article2681534.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>，導致建造工程一再被延遲。2011年8月，印度國防部向印度[[人民院_(印度)|人民院]]提交報告，對於維克蘭特艦體已經完成75%的建造工作，並將在2011年12月向首次下水，之後的工作將會進一步完成，並進行調試。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://zeenews.india.com/news/nation/indigenous-aircraft-carrier-launch-this-dec_723865.html|title=‘Indigenous aircraft carrier launch this Dec’|work=Zee News|accessdate=2016-06-29|archive-date=2015-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150609184600/http://zeenews.india.com/news/nation/indigenous-aircraft-carrier-launch-this-dec_723865.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ibnlive.in.com/generalnewsfeed/news/first-indigenous-aircraft-carrier-to-be-completed-by-dec-govt/773900.html |title=First indigenous aircraft carrier to be completed by Dec: Govt, IBN Live News<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2016-06-29 |archive-date=2012-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107013318/http://ibnlive.in.com/generalnewsfeed/news/first-indigenous-aircraft-carrier-to-be-completed-by-dec-govt/773900.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2011年12月29日，科欽造船廠（CSL）已經完成了超過14,000噸的建造工作，並將其拖出旱塢第一次下水。<ref name=bs-gears/>直至2012年下半年，船廠再次將其拖回旱塢，並繼續進行推進器和發電系統的集成工作。<ref name=DN449>{{cite web|url=http://www.defencenow.com/news/449/india-floats-out-its-first-indigenous-aircraft-carrier-ins-vikrant-from-cochin.html|title=India Floats out Its First Indigenous Aircraft Carrier 'INS Vikrant' From Cochin|work=defencenow.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213103829/http://www.defencenow.com/news/449/india-floats-out-its-first-indigenous-aircraft-carrier-ins-vikrant-from-cochin.html|archivedate=2015-02-13}}</ref><ref name=hindu-float/>

2012年7月，[[印度时报|印度时报]]（The Times of India）報導，維克蘭特號的建造工作已經拖延了三年，並且航母的調試計劃將定在2017年。後來在2012年11月，[[新德里电视台|新德里电视台]]（NDTV）報導航母的建造成本已經再度上升和至少需延遲五年才能交付[[印度海軍|印度海軍]]。這次延遲之後，預計交付印度海軍的時間將是2018年之後，對比上一次預定的2014年延遲了四年之多。<ref name="Ndtv">{{cite web|url=http://www.ndtv.com/article/india/indian-aircraft-carrier-more-costly-already-delayed-294997|title=Indian aircraft carrier: More costly, already delayed|author=Sudhi Ranjan Sen|date=20 November 2012|work=NDTV.com|accessdate=2016-06-29|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709004118/http://www.ndtv.com/article/india/indian-aircraft-carrier-more-costly-already-delayed-294997|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年8月12日在科欽造船廠（CSL）第二次下水，在下水後維克蘭特號將完成其他建造工作。根據印度[[海军中将|海军中将]]{{link-en|羅賓·當文|Robin Dhowan}}（Robin Dhowan）的說法，維克蘭特艦體的建造工作已經完成75，佔整體的83%，而維克蘭特的艦體建造有90%屬於印度國產，其中推進系統有約50%，艦載戰鬥系統則有約30%。同時他也露，維克蘭特還裝配備多功能雷達和[[近迫武器系統|近迫武器系統]]（CIWS）。2013年8月12日，維克蘭特按照A.K.安東尼的說法正式下水，並將在2016年開始進行海上試驗，2018年後期正式服役。<ref name="TOILaunch" /><ref name="NDTVLaunch">[http://www.ndtv.com/article/india/ins-vikrant-first-indian-made-aircraft-carrier-enters-water-next-week-402556 INS Vikrant, first Indian-made aircraft carrier, enters water next week] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ndtv.com/article/india/ins-vikrant-first-indian-made-aircraft-carrier-enters-water-next-week-402556 |date=20131214202405 }} NDTV 11 August 2013</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.navyrecognition.com/index.php/news/defence-news/year-2013-news/november-2013-navy-naval-forces-maritime-industry-technology-security-global-news/1357-handover-of-aircraft-carrier-ins-vikramaditya-to-take-place-on-november-16.html |title=Handover of aircraft carrier INS Vikramaditya to take place on November 16 |date=November 14, 2013 |accessdate=2016-06-29 |archive-date=2016-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805181959/http://www.navyrecognition.com/index.php/news/defence-news/year-2013-news/november-2013-navy-naval-forces-maritime-industry-technology-security-global-news/1357-handover-of-aircraft-carrier-ins-vikramaditya-to-take-place-on-november-16.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年5月28日，維克蘭特號第三次下水。

